											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Hag raises her forearm, fingers straightened to a point as if a blade and drives her hand towards the player's face. Rips her hand back, shot of the eye on her nail (maybe?) and then she either - kisses it gently or wave her hand over it (whatever is easier) and then jams it back into the player's head. " />
										</node>
